emerge as the most time-consuming step in REstretto. Since local optimization
was beyond the scope of the proof-of-concept, we implemented a simple,
hill-climbing method. However, a more sophisticated, gradient-based
optimization is warranted to highlight the real ability of the proposed
strategy.</p>
